
# Setup

Install pyenv and pyenv-virtualenv with brew.  Setup a cards env and set the local pyenv to it in the root dir.
must init pyenv with pyenv init (gives instructions to add to shell)


Install pipenv to install packages to this env 

Now you must run pyenv activate in every new shell still.

installed ipython
pip install pytest pytest-watch pytest-asyncio

Run ./make_fifo.sh
run ./open_pipes.sh once
cat > p1_in
cat p1_out

then use setup_tmux.sh to open a tmux session with the right windows

You must also set the GEMIN API KEY via
export GEMINI_API_KEY=""
DO NOT COMMIT THE ACTUAL KEY INTO THE REPOSITORY

source set_llm_env.sh
